sentences.english: This method controls the sending rate for each source node.
sentences.chinese: 這種方法控制每個信源節點的傳輸速率。

sentences.english: A single spindle should yield a transfer rate of approximately 30 small messages per second.
sentences.chinese: 一個心軸應能實現大約每秒30封小郵件的傳輸速率。

sentences.english: High performance networks can accelerate data transmission rates and minimize the need to re-send data.
sentences.chinese: 高性能網絡能加速數據傳輸速率和減少需要確認數據。

sentences.english: A wide range of data transfer rates are available, with speeds up to about 128 kilobits per second.
sentences.chinese: 提供較寬的數據傳輸速率，速率可達每秒128千位。

sentences.english: The resulting transfer rate is 110 baud .
sentences.chinese: 最終的傳輸速率是110波特。

sentences.english: A wide range of data transfer rates are available, with speeds up to about 128 kilobits per second (kBps).
sentences.chinese: 提供較寬的數據傳輸速率，速率可達每秒128千位。
